OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEU rules to force USB-C    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchargers for all phones    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Manufacturers will be forced to create 
OL,6, a universal charging solution for      
OL,7, phones and small electronic devices,   
OL,8, under a new rule proposed by the       
OL,9, European Commission (EC).              
OL,11,FThe aim is to reduce waste by          
OL,12,Fencouraging consumers to re-use        
OL,13,Fexisting chargers when buying a new    
OL,14,Fdevice.                                
OL,16,FAll smartphones sold in the EU must    
OL,17,Fhave USB-C chargers, the proposal said.
OL,19,FApple has warned such a move would harm
OL,20,Finnovation.                            
